data.value: Here you will find your schedule for the week. Each task is outlined in the handbook you received upon arrival to Alluvion. Please review and let me know if you have any follow-up questions. Remember, check your tasks so all biometric data can be processed and sent back to Mission Control. The analysis is critical to understanding the physical impact while adapting to the Alluvion environment.
